# Build context hygiene for the API/worker images.
# The Dockerfiles build from the repo root and COPY only:
#   apps/fred-evaluation-backend/{Makefile,pyproject.toml,uv.lock,README.md,fred_evaluation_backend}
#   scripts/makefiles
#   libs/fred-deepeval-cli   (worker only)
# Everything below is large or irrelevant to the build. Note: we deliberately do
# NOT ignore migrations/ — the image runs `alembic upgrade head` as a job.

# Version control
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Virtual environments and build markers (the heavy stuff)
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/target/
**/build/
**/dist/

# Python caches / artifacts
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.egg-info/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/

# Node (if any frontend is colocated)
**/node_modules/

# Local env / secrets — config is mounted at runtime, never baked in
**/.env

# OS / editor noise
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
